    "title": "Quotation: と",
    "explanation": "と marks where someone's words end. 「変だ！」とムーミンが言った — everything before と is what was said.\n\nThe pattern: [words] + と + [verb of speaking]. This works with 言う, 呼ぶ, and other communication verbs. 「ここにきて！」と呼んだ — called out (saying) 'come here!'\n\nRe-read and find every と. What words does it wrap up each time?"
